title: Global Sounds 2004 - Journey Into Music
description:
A 28-track sampler for the price of 6,99 Euros published by "Association of Dutch RecordRetailers", the NVGD, to promote WorldMusic (Global Sounds). 
It contains a booklet with 28 coupons which gave you a discount of 5,00 Euros each when buying one of the albums represented on this sampler.

Released: 2004
Genre: Folk, World, Latin
